PDO Survey Dashboard v2

Last Time of Update (IST) : 2021-10-08 11:19:29

Readme

A note

Surveys completed by Block/District gives the number of surveys done in a Block/district. GPs covered by Block/District gives the total number of GPs covered by the surveys done in each of the block/district. GPs covered >= Surveys completed as a PDO might be incharge of multiple GPs. In the earlier version Total GPs covered may exceed the Total GPs in Block and District if a PDO fills or submits the survey more than once / there is an error by the PDO in filling the right GP /Block. This version corrects for that.


Total number of surveys till now : 3126

Changelog

17/0/2021 :

  • In the earlier version Total GPs covered may exceed the Total GPs in Block and District if a PDO fills or submits the survey more than once / there is an error by the PDO in filling the right GP /Block. This version corrects for that.
  • Added GP level report - multiple surveys in GP are counted as one.
  • Added excel export buttons


Total number of surveys till now : 3126
